{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "AGENT-EUDR-019: Corruption Index Monitor Agent -- CPI score tracking, WGI governance indicators, sector bribery risk assessments, institutional quality monitoring, trend analysis, deforestation-corruption correlations, EUDR Article 29 compliance impact, and alert management",
